* Basic pseudocode for this site *

HOME PAGE
- Header navigations link to each individual web page.
- Changes nav text color on hover.
- First section of home page contains owl-carousel with autoPlayTimeout, autoPlayHoverPause features
- Second section is "About Us"
- Last section is "Menu" that links to 'Juices page' and 'Smoothies page'. Text color of links changes on hover.
- Footer section with social media links and copyright.

JUICES PAGE
- Header navigations link to each individual web page.
- Changes nav text color on hover.
- First section is cover image
- Second section contains juice menu with price.
- Footer section with social media links and copyright.

SMOOTHIES PAGE
- Similar to JUICES PAGE

CONTACT PAGE
- Header navigations link to each individual web page.
- Changes nav text color on hover.
- Contact details on the main section
- Feedback form
- Location map on the right-hand side
- Footer section with social media links and copyright.



